name: FOMO
description: I never felt like I belonged at teenage house parties, so I made a short film/video to share how I feel about it. I came up with this idea around 6 months before I posted the video, but never developed it because I was afraid of being judged as a party pooper or as a boring person. This is the piece of art/thumbnail that accompanies that video. Proudly made with Microsoft Paint. Watch the film: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cytzqTlWZq8
